item.dc:creator: @_Rich Rich
item.description:
@_Rich wrote:

it wasn’t closed earlier because no one reported this topic

OP, wait till the status page updates, your server will not be added unless it’s online and allows the Moparscape webclient to connect with the details specified when you registered the server.
